info.title: Onshape REST API
info.description: The Onshape REST API consumed by all clients.

tags.name: OpenAPI
tags.description: Endpoints for getting the OpenAPI specification for the Onshape API.

get.summary: OpenAPI spec documentation for the Onshape REST API.

parameters.name: fileType
parameters.description: The type of file to return. Defaults to JSON.

parameters.name: excludedTags
parameters.description: If an operation contains an excluded tag, it is not returned from this endpoint.

parameters.name: includedTags
parameters.description: Return only operations with tags included in includedTags.

parameters.name: documentationStatus
parameters.description: Only return endpoints that have the specified document status. Default is to return all the endpoints the user should have access to.

parameters.name: wvm
parameters.description: One of w or v or m corresponding to whether a workspace or version or microversion was entered.

parameters.name: featureId
parameters.description: ID of a feature; repeat query param to add more than one

parameters.name: linkDocumentId
parameters.description: Id of document that links to the document being accessed. This may provide additional access rights to the document. Allowed only with version (v) path parameter.

parameters.name: noSketchGeometry
parameters.description: Whether or not to output simple sketch info without geometry

scopes.OAuth2ReadPII: Application can read your profile information
scopes.OAuth2Write: Application can write to your documents
scopes.OAuth2Delete: Application can delete your documents and workspaces
scopes.OAuth2Purchase: Application can request purchases on your behalf
scopes.OAuth2Share: Application can share and unshare documents on your behalf
